Activity flow:
    (/start request)
    1. We first recieve a start request
    2. check if the start request associates with a username
    3. if it does goto sendGame()
    // Here the start command is triggered for the first time for the username
    4. register him/her in the Visitors
    5. register his/her inviter data (if any)
    6. goto prepareRegisteration()

    sendGame:
        send that god damn game
    
    prepareRegisteration:
        ask user for the username

    